com.google.api.client.http
Class LogContent

java.lang.Object
  com.google.api.client.http.LogContent
All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpContent
final class LogContent
extends java.lang.Object
implements HttpContent

Wraps another source of HTTP content without modifying the content, but also possibly logging this content.

Content is only logged if Level.CONFIG is loggable.

Author:
Yaniv Inbar
